  "title": "Much More Dungeons",
  "description": "Explore the overworld for tower dungeons packed with loot, supplies, and rare rewards",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"Much More Dungeons banner\" />\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Discord&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord badge\" />\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=YouTube&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=youtube&logoColor=white\" alt=\"YouTube badge\" />\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=GitHub&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=github&logoColor=white\" alt=\"GitHub badge\" />\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=CurseForge&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=white\" alt=\"CurseForge badge\" />\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Modrinth&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Modrinth badge\" />\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Documentation&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=read-the-docs&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Documentation badge\" />\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"section divider\" />\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cximTtw.png\" alt=\"decorative divider\" />\n</p>\n\n**Much More Dungeons** adds handcrafted dungeon content to Minecraft 1.20.1 with support for Fabric and Forge.  \nIt introduces a surface tower dungeon designed for exploration and early-to-mid game progression.\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/nightbeamstudio\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c14e387dab576fe667689cf/670f5a0171bfb928b21a7e00_support_me_on_kofi_beige.png\" alt=\"Support on Ko-fi\" />\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n---\n\n## Features\n\n- Adds Tower Dungeon structure to world generation  \n- Supports Fabric and Forge (1.20.1)  \n- Handcrafted NBT structure layout  \n- Spawns in multiple overworld biomes  \n- Uses jigsaw system for stable generation  \n- Balanced progression-based loot  \n\n---\n\n## Dungeon\n\n- Surface overworld structure  \n- Designed as a natural landmark  \n- Built for exploration and survival gameplay  \n- Loot includes ores, food, and enchanted items  \n\n---\n\n## Loot\n\nChests contain balanced rewards:\n- Early survival supplies  \n- Mid-game resources  \n- Rare items for exploration rewards  \n\n---\n\n## Media\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ujTrbXc.png\" alt=\"Tower dungeon exterior\" />\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FFeQjkB.png\" alt=\"Tower dungeon interior corridor\" />\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/SuFE8Mu.png\" alt=\"Dungeon room view\" />\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/3DYM4jV.png\" alt=\"Loot chest inside dungeon\" />\n</p>\n\n---\n\n## Compatibility\n\n- Minecraft 1.20.1 (26.1)  \n- Fabric  \n- Forge  \n\n---\n\n## Links\n\n- Discord: https://discord.gg/TJc3CxR4jK  \n- GitHub: https://github.com/MeherBenSalem  \n- CurseForge: https://www.curseforge.com/members/nightbeamstudio/projects  \n- Modrinth: https://modrinth.com/organization/nightbeam  \n\n---\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/nightbeam\">\n    <img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/db9c3eef-25e8-4ac0-93b6-bf386644dcef.webp\" alt=\"BisectHosting partner banner\" />\n  </a>\n</p>",
